---
title: Brazilian Style Fish Moqueca with Zesty Rice and Chilli Flakes
description: Influenced by Afro-Brazilian culture, moqueca is a versatile seafood stew. It starts with onion, garlic and tomato, before coconut milk, chilli and lime are added. There's many versions of moqueca, but fish ones like our dish are the most famous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R48_W41_UK_R19724-5_MAIN_low_2-b5d84b5d.jpg
